name: Minton H
text: A tiny takeout or delivery only location. Staff are really friendly. The food is absolutely delicious and service is usually quick and on time. They have wing street here and the deals are quite good.

name: Melida Decarlo
text: The best delivery, just a little pricey. They have great crust, and sauce. The cheese is the best though

name: Debra Skinner
text: Ordering was great online. Delivery was good.  The pizza was very skimpy on toppings and almost no cheese.  And the Hershey cookie was burnt. I've always loved pizza hut but I may never order again.

name: Hari Gudapati
text: Bought vegetable pizza. It was excellent. Also buffalo wings. Really horrible and tasted like uncooked and just got reheated a frozen ones. Clean store.

name: Najja Hose
text: Great deals and good food from a friendly staff.

name: Cristina Villalpando
text: I order a deliver and I got my pizza like someone step on it I have a picture I wish I could put it so everyone see it

name: Daniel HARRIS
text: pizza was dry and missing lotta cheese  was a really sad pizza

name: William Hogan
text: Pizza missing cheese over 20 percent of top and was over cooked IMO.. Should have went to Little Caesars like my wife suggested.
